<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA17">
<l>cūḻntaṭiyār vēṇṭiṉakkā ṟōṉṟātu viṭṭālum</l>
<l>vāḻntiṭuvar piṉṉuntam vāytiṟavār cūḻnteṅkum</l>
<l>vāḷvaraikaṭ pōlarakkaṉ vaṉṟalaika ṭāmiṭiya</l>
<l>tāḷvaraivil lēntiṉār tām.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who, although at the time the servants around [him] wanted [it] he left [them alone],</l>
<l>not appearing, does not open his mouth even afterwards for those who have lived,</l>
<l>he stretched out without measure [his] foot so that the strong heads of the Rakṣasa</l>
<l>crumbled like bright mountains all around.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
